SpoonerPlacements.Note: Last thing you knew, you were joining the solo mile high club in a freefalling Super car above the business district. You blink, and you're piloting a jet fighter straight into a wall. Blink again, and you're not quite sure if this is a rocket-powered Super car or a flimsy ultralight. Either you're on one hell of a come down, or the fun's just getting started. Transform Race starting in Super cars, also featuring the Molotok, Rocket Voltic, Ultralight and Parachutes.
